Changes in WolfEdit 2.0.4¥ The only change in this version is the contents of the About box, which has been updated to reflect the change in status of the Full version from shareware to freeware.Changes in WolfEdit 2.0.2¥ A bug introduced in 2.0.1 causing levels added to an existing scenario not to be saved properly has been fixed.Changes in WolfEdit 2.0.1¥ Limits imposed by Wolfenstein 3D on the number of objects and enemies in one room or in one level are now checked properly. You will be warned if these limits are exceeded when you close or save a level.¥ A bug which could potentially cause crashes has been fixed.¥ The Ghost and Get Psyched artwork is now loaded properly when opening a previously saved scenario.